{"tid":753644,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母咁撚多廣告","createTime":"2018-07-23T18:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T07:31:35.000Z","uid":130119,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"76235826d62998358687497ab64f9eb99e563b27","tid":753644,"uid":130119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T18:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/024030_d6cdebc9f854f001af4dba1036b52359.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F024030_d6cdebc9f854f001af4dba1036b52359.png&h=b4af10c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身你話睇youtube 有個廣告放開頭都話接受到 起碼等5秒就有得飛 <br />\n<br />\n而家開youtube幾分鐘條片有2-3個廣告插係中間 屌你老母洗唔洗咁倡狂啊 睇幾分鐘又停幾秒 睇幾分鐘又停幾秒 睇廣告定睇片啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日話adblock搞到無廣告費收網站又話無收入乜乜柒柒  自己搞成咁真係抵撚你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n利申本身電腦chrome不嬲有adblock 近排轉左睇手機板先發現原來廣告已經做到咁撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻上網搵手機版adblock<br />\n<br />\n竟然會有中學同學仲未知乜野係adblock 到底佢地點生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d434ac7e8ccb971a75c2566f092e2abd521ecbc4","tid":753644,"uid":152047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T19:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔明youtube facebook啲廣告要插係片中間。<br />\n一係頭播，一係尾播，再唔係你擺出面周圍咁多位，<br />\n都好過睇睇吓播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時賺咁多都唔夠"},{"pid":"4349aa5d9268e62a792e7ec4939c72a9136be466","tid":753644,"uid":191510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d434ac7e8ccb971a75c2566f092e2abd521ecbc4","tid":753644,"uid":152047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T19:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔明youtube facebook啲廣告要插係片中間。<br />\n一係頭播，一係尾播，再唔係你擺出面周圍咁多位，<br />\n都好過睇睇吓播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時賺咁多都唔夠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T19:14:07.000Z","msg":"好似係個片主自己決定???"},{"pid":"9763cebad576ff99aa5e02245f1d035a8093a0d1","tid":753644,"uid":61330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T19:21:08.000Z","msg":"可唔可以share 個app名<br />\n我打adblock有幾個都唔知邊個係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62f818cf3ad156cbebb148793aa360b8365f800","tid":753644,"uid":173480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9763cebad576ff99aa5e02245f1d035a8093a0d1","tid":753644,"uid":61330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T19:21:08.000Z","msg":"可唔可以share 個app名<br />\n我打adblock有幾個都唔知邊個係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T19:50:06.000Z","msg":"我之前買咗個adblock無料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nYouTube, Twitch, 乜嘢廣告都block唔到"},{"pid":"df889a0eb3830c3b0030df19e96cabadc0bf4089","tid":753644,"uid":130119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9763cebad576ff99aa5e02245f1d035a8093a0d1","tid":753644,"uid":61330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T19:21:08.000Z","msg":"可唔可以share 個app名<br />\n我打adblock有幾個都唔知邊個係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T21:07:47.000Z","msg":"我個隻就咁叫adblock 原理大概係用vpn既方法去block 不過有時個vpn會炒左搞到上唔到網 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/050621_d8b4069dd76bbfc891deea08acbe8072.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F050621_d8b4069dd76bbfc891deea08acbe8072.png&h=27047866&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b13e0ea44ea04c46246763ec411018812abdf6f3","tid":753644,"uid":173480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df889a0eb3830c3b0030d